spec_data.Name: texlive-actuarialangle
spec_data.Description:
The package defines a single command \actuarialangle to typeset
"angles" in the 'present value of an annuity' symbols common in
actuarial and financial notation.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Sun 06 Aug 2017 07:45:39 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Symbol for use in "present value" statements of an annuity
